My AMA earlier today got archived for who knows what reason... 
About my Jr modship.
I was a Jr. Mod for a week and was demoted for not putting enough time into moderating (I blame ssb and hyrule warriors coming out on that week D:)

So let's see if this will get archived or not... AMA

@kycrafft(from last post) Probably not as they require you to be active as fuqqqqqq.
